    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Educational institutions in Britain or in a system based on or similar to Britain's, where students in the last two years of secondary school study for entry into advanced schools, including preparation for qualifying exams such as A-levels, GCSEs, etc.</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
        <Note_Contributors>
